585
00:24:28,560 --> 00:24:29,400
Don’t do this!

586
00:24:29,420 --> 00:24:29,780
Brother!

587
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:30,280
No,

588
00:24:30,360 --> 00:24:31,400
leader, leader!

589
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:32,360
I’m wrong.

590
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,640
You can't report me to the officer and

591
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,600
put me in jail.

592
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:35,560
I will not do this again.

593
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:37,880
It’s not just me.

594
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:38,480
Them!

595
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:42,320
Jin Quan’er, Zhang Chaohe, Xiao Shen’er

596
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:43,400
are all involved.

597
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:44,040
They took it, too.

598
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:45,200
Gao Yunfu, don't talk nonsense!

599
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:45,880
Gao Yunfu,

600
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,000
don't wrong good people!

601
00:24:47,040 --> 00:24:47,920
You are slurring!

602
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:48,480
Leader,

603
00:24:48,760 --> 00:24:49,680
he insults us.

604
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,360
We are wronged!

605
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,240
We are wronged!

606
00:24:52,280 --> 00:24:53,160
What's wrong?

607
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,440
We spent the money together.

608
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:04,600
I…

609
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,960
Shuiyun Theater is really a den of thieves.

610
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:09,320
Dasheng,

611
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:12,120
take them all to the police station.

612
00:25:13,040 --> 00:25:13,960
Leader!

613
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:14,880
Leader!

614
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,000
Leader!

615
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,000
Leader!

616
00:25:17,040 --> 00:25:17,760
-Don't move!
-I am wrong.

617
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:19,360
I'm really wrong.

618
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:20,520
Leader!

619
00:25:20,560 --> 00:25:21,800
Please show some mercy!

620
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:23,800
Forgive me!

621
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:24,680
I’ll never

622
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:26,200
do this again!

623
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:28,200
We grew up together.

624
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,240
Forgive me!

625
00:25:29,280 --> 00:25:30,480
I will turn over a new leaf.

626
00:25:30,480 --> 00:25:31,680
-Leader!
-I will turn over a new leaf.

627
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:34,880
Brothers,

628
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:36,520
don't cry.

629
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,200
This is good.

630
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:41,280
After we get to the police station,

631
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,680
we’ll just be in jail for a few years.

632
00:25:44,360 --> 00:25:47,840
Use these years to change our freedom for life.

633
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:49,640
Don’t you think it’s worthwhile?

634
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:51,480
It is.

635
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:54,760
Guys,

636
00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:56,320
do you see?

637
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:59,480
If you want to be free in the future,

638
00:26:00,280 --> 00:26:01,800
you know what to do.

639
00:26:03,840 --> 00:26:06,440
You can keep ruining the Shuiyun Theater.

640
00:26:07,280 --> 00:26:10,720
He dares not kill anyone.

641
00:26:26,560 --> 00:26:27,760
You would rather go to jail

642
00:26:28,600 --> 00:26:30,240
than stay in Shuiyun Theater.

643
00:26:31,080 --> 00:26:31,960
Yes!

644
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:34,960
If it weren't for the life-long contract in your hand,

645
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:37,880
I would have changed my career and made a fortune.

646
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:40,360
I want to leave but I can’t.

647
00:26:41,560 --> 00:26:43,160
You are holding me back from living a good life.

648
00:26:43,840 --> 00:26:45,240
Who am I going to steal from except you?

649
00:26:45,760 --> 00:26:47,440
You owe me.

650
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:50,420
You deserve it!

651
00:26:50,540 --> 00:26:51,480
You deserve it!

652
00:26:51,600 --> 00:26:52,080
Dasheng.

653
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:52,840
What are you doing?

654
00:26:52,840 --> 00:26:53,560
Send them to the police station!

655
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:54,880
No need to listen to him.

656
00:26:55,760 --> 00:26:56,360
Leader!

657
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,200
Forgive me!

658
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:57,720
Leader!

659
00:26:57,760 --> 00:26:58,160
Let's go.

660
00:26:58,160 --> 00:26:58,760
Please forgive me!

661
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:00,640
I will do my best!

662
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:02,280
Leader!

663
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:08,240
Leader!

664
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:10,240
Don’t get angry with him. We…

665
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,360
I'm tired and want to sleep.

666
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:30,480
It's all your fault, bitch.

667
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:31,400
-Would you cut it out?
-What are you doing?

668
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,640
We didn't steal.

669
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:35,960
La Yuehong,

670
00:27:37,360 --> 00:27:38,960
accompany me back to the house to pack things up.

671
00:27:47,340 --> 00:27:50,380
♫ Pshaw ♫

672
00:27:50,620 --> 00:27:51,860
♫ Mr. Gao ♫

673
00:27:51,980 --> 00:27:57,300
♫ Who will spend the night with you ♫

674
00:27:57,580 --> 00:27:59,780
♫ Lady, don’t be annoyed ♫

675
00:27:59,780 --> 00:28:05,460
♫ This liquor is brewed by the officials overnight ♫

676
00:28:05,580 --> 00:28:09,420
♫ Thus it’s named “Overnight Liquor” ♫

677
00:28:09,940 --> 00:28:10,940
♫ Well ♫

678
00:28:10,940 --> 00:28:16,540
♫ Pass me ♫

679
00:28:16,540 --> 00:28:18,020
♫ Yes, Your Ladyship ♫

680
00:28:19,140 --> 00:28:24,820
♫ Overnight Liquor ♫

681
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:25,880
Madam,

682
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:26,800
are you looking for me?

683
00:28:34,080 --> 00:28:35,560
Fengtai sang

684
00:28:35,760 --> 00:28:36,480
and hummed

685
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:37,680
when he came home today.

686
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:40,600
He is not a man loves operas.

687
00:28:41,040 --> 00:28:42,480
I keep wondering

688
00:28:42,840 --> 00:28:45,240
what did he do last night?

689
00:28:46,840 --> 00:28:47,840
He

690
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:49,080
played cards at Mr. Huang's.

691
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:51,560
Maybe they

692
00:28:52,040 --> 00:28:53,760
called the troupe to liven things up.

693
00:28:53,800 --> 00:28:54,920
Last time I asked you,

694
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,640
you also said they played cards.

695
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:02,240
Are you afraid that I’ll quarrel with Fengtai

696
00:29:02,360 --> 00:29:04,760
and you’ll catch up in the middle?

697
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:06,680
Madam,

698
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:08,560
Mr. Cheng didn't play cards yesterday.

699
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:10,240
After coming out of the freight agency,

700
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:13,120
he went to the theater.

701
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:14,480
Then?

702
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:15,600
Then…

703
00:29:16,160 --> 00:29:18,760
Then he went for a cup of coffee

704
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:24,320
and

705
00:29:25,520 --> 00:29:27,520
rested in the theater.

706
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:30,600
Which theater?

707
00:29:33,640 --> 00:29:34,840
Shuiyun Theater.

708
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:37,560
All right.

709
00:29:37,560 --> 00:29:38,160
OK.

710
00:29:38,560 --> 00:29:39,200
You can leave.

711
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:45,800
Madam,

712
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:48,920
these actresses are all vulgar.

713
00:29:49,080 --> 00:29:50,880
Mr. Cheng is just looking for some new faces.

714
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,160
He won't take it seriously.

715
00:29:52,280 --> 00:29:54,080
You don't need to be angry.

716
00:30:02,760 --> 00:30:03,640
Dad,

717
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:06,240
I am so tired.

718
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:08,240
I don't want to worry about it anymore.

719
00:30:09,160 --> 00:30:10,160
No way.

720
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:12,280
You are a member of Shang family.

721
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:13,580
The troupe

722
00:30:13,580 --> 00:30:14,800
and the theater stage

723
00:30:14,840 --> 00:30:16,040
are burdens

724
00:30:16,040 --> 00:30:17,880
on your shoulder.

725
00:30:20,420 --> 00:30:20,940
Dad,

726
00:30:21,360 --> 00:30:22,600
I'm cold and tired.

727
00:30:23,120 --> 00:30:24,360
I can't hang on.

728
00:30:24,560 --> 00:30:26,760
Keep going.

729
00:30:27,760 --> 00:30:30,360
Hang on there.

730
00:30:30,760 --> 00:30:32,760
How to become the protagonist

731
00:30:32,760 --> 00:30:34,360
if you don’t persevere.

732
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,600
I can't do it.

733
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:40,360
If you keep forcing me,

734
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:41,960
I'm going to drown myself in the river.

735
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:43,480
Don’t seek death.

736
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:45,040
That is throwing in the towel.

737
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:51,360
Death, death.

738
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:52,560
Doing it again?

739
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:55,200
I will beat you to death!

740
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:56,720
I will beat you to death!

741
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:09,600
Kid,

742
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:11,520
you listen to me.

743
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,520
Tell me,

744
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:15,880
do you want

745
00:31:16,320 --> 00:31:17,960
to be free

746
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:19,680
without people hitting you again?

747
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:21,640
No one will care about you anymore.

748
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:28,880
Fine.

749
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:32,360
Then we have to

750
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,040
work our butts off.

751
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:37,640
Let me tell you,

752
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:39,680
in this world,

753
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,200
as long as you are

754
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:43,160
a little better than others,

755
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,280
they will be jealous of you,

756
00:31:45,520 --> 00:31:46,520
put you in danger,

757
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:48,360
ruin your life,

758
00:31:48,360 --> 00:31:50,560
drag you down desperately, and

759
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:51,640
break you.

760
00:31:52,760 --> 00:31:53,640
But

761
00:31:54,560 --> 00:31:55,520
if you are better than others

762
00:31:55,520 --> 00:31:57,000
by a large margin,

763
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,920
no one can catch up with you.

764
00:31:59,360 --> 00:32:00,360
Guess what?

765
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:02,560
They will respect you,

766
00:32:03,360 --> 00:32:04,400
afraid of you,

767
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:06,000
love you,

768
00:32:06,120 --> 00:32:08,440
and treat you like a venerable master.

769
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:14,320
So from now on,

770
00:32:15,760 --> 00:32:17,840
no matter what obstacles you are running into,

771
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:19,400
you have to tell yourself

772
00:32:19,520 --> 00:32:21,000
confidently

773
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:22,400
that you can carry on.

774
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:26,280
Once you tide it over,

775
00:32:27,520 --> 00:32:29,520
and when you look back,

776
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,640
these are all trivial matters.

777
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:36,800
From now on,

778
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:40,000
you will be free

779
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,760
and be the king.

780
00:32:46,760 --> 00:32:48,240
Let me ask you again,

781
00:32:50,520 --> 00:32:51,840
do you want to throw in the towel?

782
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:15,240
You should be content that Shuiyun Theater didn’t let you pay penalty.

783
00:33:16,560 --> 00:33:18,000
How dare you steal?

784
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:20,720
And also,

785
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:22,520
this new coat you are wearing

786
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:24,240
was paid by the Leader for the actors of Shuiyun Theater

787
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:28,160
during the Spring Festival last year.

788
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:31,480
You are no longer a member of Shuiyun Theater.

789
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,560
Why do you still have the face to wear it?

790
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:35,560
You won’t let her wear coat in such a cold day?

791
00:33:35,560 --> 00:33:36,680
Do you want to freeze her to death?

792
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:37,840
She asks for it.

793
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:39,800
Let her borne the consequences.

794
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:13,840
Sister,

795
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:15,400
you are pregnant.

796
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,400
Don't get cold.

797
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:20,520
Let's go.

798
00:34:30,199 --> 00:34:30,840
Sister,

799
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:32,440
this is my monthly pay.

800
00:34:32,880 --> 00:34:34,480
Go out and get a rickshaw.

801
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:36,520
If the Xue family gives you a hard time,

802
00:34:37,199 --> 00:34:38,520
don't do anything stupid.

803
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:40,800
I will support you with my earnings.

804
00:34:48,520 --> 00:34:49,920
Good brother.

805
00:34:51,239 --> 00:34:52,639
Your friendship

806
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:55,679
is kept in my heart.

807
00:35:27,080 --> 00:35:28,080
Leader.

808
00:35:31,640 --> 00:35:33,240
I know

809
00:35:33,520 --> 00:35:35,680
that if you hadn’t asked for a favor from the old leader,

810
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:39,440
I wouldn't have had enough to eat.

811
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:42,520
I know

812
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:46,360
it's for my own good that you won't let me go.

813
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:51,200
But the mother and child are connected, leader.

814
00:35:53,120 --> 00:35:55,160
I can't bear being apart from my child.

815
00:35:58,840 --> 00:35:59,960
No matter how good

816
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,640
Shuiyun Theater is,

817
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:06,840
it is not my home after all.

818
00:36:10,240 --> 00:36:12,840
Thanks for your care all these years.

819
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:15,760
I’m really grateful for

820
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:18,760
your kindness.

821
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:22,600
I’ll repay your kindness in the future.

822
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,400
Why don't you follow her?

823
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:23,440
Why come back?

824
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:24,800
Who are you showing your sad face to?

825
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,800
Ever since sister finished her apprenticeship,

826
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:33,040
have you treated her nicely?

827
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:35,160
Isn’t it because she looks better than you

828
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:36,200
and sings better than you?

829
00:37:36,450 --> 00:37:36,960
Bah!

830
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:37,560
Do you think she…

831
00:37:37,560 --> 00:37:38,880
Enough! Enough!

832
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:42,240
Just spare your words.

833
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:46,240
Leader!

834
00:37:54,640 --> 00:37:55,280
Leader!

835
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,000
Leader!

836
00:37:56,640 --> 00:37:57,520
Leader!

837
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:03,960
Leader!

838
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,120
Leader!

839
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,480
What are you doing?

840
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:13,680
Why are you here?

841
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:14,440
Get up.

842
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:15,640
What happened?

843
00:38:15,720 --> 00:38:16,280
Stand up.

844
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,160
What did you say?

845
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:20,220
Everything is gone. Everything is gone.

846
00:38:20,430 --> 00:38:22,350
Everything is gone. Everything is gone.

847
00:38:22,680 --> 00:38:24,000
- Everything is gone.
-What are you talking about?

848
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,400
What is going on?

849
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:26,680
-Get up.
- What is going on?

850
00:38:26,720 --> 00:38:27,320
Leader!

851
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,840
Leader, don't scare us.

852
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:30,320
If you feel bad, you can cry out.

853
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:31,760
Don't hold back.

854
00:38:32,040 --> 00:38:33,320
That's right, leader.

855
00:38:33,530 --> 00:38:34,120
What to do?

856
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:34,800
Oh, no!

857
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:35,640
He’s not normal.

858
00:38:35,680 --> 00:38:36,600
I'm afraid it will be worse.

859
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:38,280
Don’t you think he looks

860
00:38:38,320 --> 00:38:39,640
like the one in the Pingyang Tower…

861
00:38:39,920 --> 00:38:40,840
Stop talking.

862
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:41,720
It’s scary.

863
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:43,200
Everything is gone.

864
00:38:43,200 --> 00:38:43,880
Leader!

865
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:44,920
It’s OK.

866
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:46,400
This is no big deal.

867
00:38:46,440 --> 00:38:48,040
We can tighten our belts.

868
00:38:48,200 --> 00:38:49,840
There will always be a solution for a few days.

869
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:50,920
That's right.

870
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:58,800
Leader, leader, leader!

871
00:38:58,840 --> 00:39:00,360
Come out!

872
00:39:03,120 --> 00:39:03,960
Too tight!

873
00:39:04,120 --> 00:39:04,960
It’s okay.

